 The late Chief of Staff to President Muhammadu Buhari, Abba Kyari, will be buried on Saturday (today) in Abuja. Personal Assistant on New Media to President Buhari, Basir Ahmad, made this known on his Twitter handle on Saturday morning. He said, “Mallam Abba Kyari will be buried later today in Abuja according to Islamic rites.”v



